data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the Hanceville school district! This full brick residence exudes charm and warmth, featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a spacious 1650 sq ft floor plan. One of its standout features is the large master suite and the expansive backyard, providing the perfect canvas for outdoor living and entertaining. Step inside, you'll find a well-appointed layout with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, offering flexibility for a growing family or those in need of extra space. The true gem of this property is the generously sized backyard. Imagine creating lasting memories in this vast outdoor space - from weekend barbecues to gatherings with friends and family. The possibilities are endless for creating your own oasis or garden retreat. Call today to schedule a showing.
